devdoc.author: https://github.com/parthvshah
devdoc.details: Contract for the 'X Alpha Token' Used as a token for all services by Variable Labs. Compliant with the ERC20 standards. https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-20

approve(address,uint256).details: Function to approve an address to spend some tokens

params._spender: @param _value @return success Function changes the allowance limit of a specified address by a fixed value.  Emits an 'Approval' event.

params._initialSupply: Assigns the initial supply to the owner of the contract. Sets the totalSupply to the initialSupply. Sets the decimals, owner and creationTime parameters.

transfer(address,uint256).details: Function to transfer funds from the owner to an account

params._to: @param _value @return success Function to transfer specified number of tokenss from the owner to a specified address. Changes the balances of both accounts and emits a 'Transfer' event.

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).details: Function to transfer funds from the owner to an account

params._from: @param _to @param _value @return success Function to transfer specified number of tokenss from the owner to a specified address. Requires the value to be lesser than the balance of the sender, allowance limit of the sender. Changes the balances of both accounts, changes the allowance limit and emits a 'Transfer' event.
